title: Paul McCartney - Tokyo Dome (Nov-21-2013)
description:
Paul McCartney - Out There Tokyo Japan 2013 (Source: 

NTSC Blu-ray BD-R)

From web site description: 

Astounding pro-shot quality, excellent performance, 

highly recommended. Picture Format: Proper 16x9 

widescreen. 

Recorded live at the Tokyo Dome in Japan, November 

21st, 2013, aired on the Japanese SkyPerfectTV! Network 

on saturday, March 22, 2014.  Complete concert 

broadcast from HD1080p source plus surprise footage!
